      "Keep Maturity sector overweight given rising yields and consumer expectations showing economic uncertainty ahead of binary catalyst"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
      "Consumer 1-year gas price expectations spiked to 9.4% from 4.1% in February, signaling stagflation fears building ahead of Iran deadline.",
